'''dribble''' [[transitive]]
# to let [[something]] fall in drips
# in various ball games, to move the ball, by repeated light [[kick]]s

===Noun===
'''dribble'''

# A [[weak]], [[unsteady]] stream; a trickle.
# A [[small]] [[amount]] of a liquid.
# In sport, the [[act]] of dribbling.

